reviewText: An amazing woman, artist, naturalist, and story writer.  She lived ahead of her time.
Beatrix Potter was an enigmatic, diversely talented individual.  This is an excellent video.  It's too bad the sound quality is so bad.

I would say this 41 min. movie is informative and gets right to the point.  Its short and sweet.  However, I believe that they could have added about 20 more min. worth of information to fill up and hour.  Beatrix Potter was really, truly an interesting woman.
